				<div id="q1form">
					<small class="formtextsmall">WeFit Health Professional is a way for health professionals to grow their digital brand and business. Professionals can connect with people in their community that they otherwise wouldn't have been able to reach to provide professional services such as diet plan, workout plans, mental health conditioning and more.</small>
				</div>
