				<div id="q2form">
					<small class="formtextsmall">Yes, you must be licensed and/or certified to conduct professional services in the state you are registered.</small>
				</div>
				<br>
				<p id="q3">What should I set my service rates at?</p>
				<div id="q3form">
					<small class="formtextsmall">Professionals may set their service rates at whatever they want, however we want these services to be relatively affordable so that we can reach all populations.</small>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col hp-col col-complementary" role="complementary">
				<p id="q4">How much does a health professional account cost?</p>
				<div id="q4form">
					<small class="formtextsmall">WeFit Health Professional is <strong>FREE</strong>. We take a service fee of 15% on all services completed through our platform. For example, if a user pays a professional $40 for a meal plan, the health professional would receive $34 while WeFit would receive $6.</small>
				</div>
				<br>
				<p id="q5">What type of health professionals are accepted?</p>
